snippet.title: Among The Sleep - Enhanced Edition
snippet.description: The Enhanced Edition of Among the Sleep will be launched digitally for PC, Mac & Linux November 2, 2017. Console versions TBA. The Enhanced Edition will be a free upgrade for existing owners of the game.
